<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>About Us</title>
    </head>

    <body>

        <!-- Center the content vertically on the page -->
       <div class="center-vertical">
        <!-- The main about-us section with a light background -->
            <div class="about-us bg-light">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <!-- First column with a picture header -->
                        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
                            <div class="pic-header">
                                <img src="about-page-pic1.jpg">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Second column with the About WoofWalk text -->
                        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                            <h2 class="header-text">
                                About WoofWalk 
                            </h2>
                            <div class="break-small mb-2"></div>
                            <p class="paragraph">
                                At WoofWalk, we believe every dog deserves the chance to get out, 
                                get exercise, and have fun - even when their owners can't be there. 
                                That's why we've built a team of experienced, passionate dog walkers 
                                dedicated to providing the best possible care for the pups in our community.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <br><br><br><br><br>

                    <div class="row">
                        <!-- First column with the Our Story text -->
                        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
                            <h2 class="header-text">
                                Our Story 
                            </h2>
                            <div class="break-small mb-2"></div>
                            <p class="paragraph">
                                WoofWalk was founded by dog lovers who saw a need for reliable, 
                                personalized dog walking services in our local area. As pet owners ourselves, 
                                we know how difficult it can be to balance work, family, and other commitments 
                                while also ensuring our furry friends get the exercise and attention they need. 
                                That's why we created WoofWalk - to be the trusted, go-to resource for busy pet 
                                parents who want to make sure their dogs are happy and healthy.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Second column with a picture header -->
                        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
                            <div class="pic-header">
                                <img src="about-page-pic2.jpg">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                    </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
       </div>

    </body>
    
</html>

